    "_comments": [
      "Runtime Actions demo #3 — the classic query+LLM pattern.",
      "Uses a shipped prompt ('Runtime Demo: Summarize Entity Records') so",
      "the prompt itself is version-controlled, review-able, and reusable",
      "by other Runtime actions that agents may author later."
    ],
    "fields": {
      "Name": "Summarize Entity Records",
      "Description": "Queries a sample of records from the specified entity, passes them to an AI prompt, and returns a structured summary with key themes and suggested follow-up questions. Exercises the `rv` + `ai` bridge namespaces — the most common composition agents reach for.",
